---
const title = "The 501(c)(3) Partnership";
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>{title} | JaiSellers Companies</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 0;
        background: #f7f7f8;
        color: #111;
      }
      header {
        background: #0c2340;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 48px 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      header h1 {
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        font-size: 2.1rem;
      }
      main {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 28px 20px;
      }
      .callout {
        margin-top: 18px;
        padding: 16px;
        background: #eef2f7;
        border-left: 4px solid #0c2340;
        border-radius: 8px;
      }
      .callout strong {
        color: #0c2340;
      }
      a {
        color: #0c2340;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      footer {
        margin-top: 40px;
        background: #082138;
        color: #fff;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 18px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <header>
      <h1>{title}</h1>
      <p>
        A guided, collaborative partnership to build your nonprofit the right way —
        from foundation to fundability.
      </p>
    </header>

    <main>
      <p>
        This partnership is for organizations already doing the work — but lacking
        the structure funders expect.
      </p>

      <div class="callout">
        <p>
          <strong>Organizations that complete this partnership become fundable.</strong>
        </p>
        <p>
          Not because of a single grant, but because they finally have the structure
          funders require.
        </p>
        <p>
          We do not build nonprofits overnight to meet last-minute grant deadlines.
          We build organizations correctly so grants don’t become emergencies.
        </p>
        <p><strong>The order matters:</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>Foundation — mission, governance, bylaws, board roles</li>
          <li>Operations — compliance, documentation, financial controls</li>
          <li>Funding — grants pursued from readiness, not panic</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <p style="margin-top: 24px;">
        <a href="/">← Back to Home</a>
      </p>
    </main>

    <footer>
      © {new Date().getFullYear()} JaiSellers Companies
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
